message: Hello Bob, I'm pleased to offer you our product today. Based on the market value and the unique benefits this product will bring to your business, I'm offering it at $1100000. This represents a significant value considering the product's worth of $1200000 to your operations, giving you an immediate $100000 in value. I believe this is a fair price that works well for both of us, allowing you to realize substantial benefits while also compensating us fairly for the product.
